commentText: In a standalone setup there is no support for placeholder values embedded in_request mappings. This method allows manually provided placeholder values so they_can be resolved. Alternatively consider creating a test that initializes a_{@link WebApplicationContext}._@since 4.2.8
codeText: public StandaloneMockMvcBuilder addPlaceholderValue(String name, String value) {_		this.placeholderValues.put(name, value)__		return this__	}

codeText: public StandaloneMockMvcBuilder addPlaceholderValue(String name, String value) {_		this.placeholderValues.put(name, value)__		return this__	}
